    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5402321>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5402327>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5402313>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5402317> ;
